p: Thus, what is essential at this point is to examine if there had been periods for which COVID-19 cases and deaths in Italy correlated with Google query data. The following time frames were selected: March 2-9, March 2-10, March 2-11, March 2-12, March 2-13, March 2-13, March 2-14, March 2-15, March 2-16, and March 2-17.
